                  Why Should You Build a Website with Tripod?

It's Perfect for Small Business

   With the time you save by using Tripod to build your
   professional-looking website, you'll have more time to spend focusing
   on your customers.

The Powerful Addons

   Simply drag-and-drop photo albums, social feeds, e-commerce widgets and
   more to make your website interactive and unique.

Mobile Ready Websites

   Expand your reach with an optimized website layout for desktop
   computers, tablets, mobile & other small screen devices.

